{"tid":2131394,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇Ching覺得京都腔完全係標準語既上位互換","createTime":"2020-07-29T23:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T15:38:57.000Z","uid":105678,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"38c7723c46b5cd987adc2a6b6034964205bb2286","tid":2131394,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T23:58:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NA8xZIy51Ko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNA8xZIy51Ko&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e3394b78\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NA8xZIy51Ko</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝哂：おおきに＝ありがとう<br />\n<br />\n唔得：あかん＝だめだ<br />\n<br />\n好：ええ＝いい<br />\n<br />\n第一句就咁睇都覺得有文化、含蓄啲。<br />\nあかん又比標準語嘅駄目就更有歷史感。<br />\nえ發音又冇い咁高聲調，順耳啲，同一個意思但表現得溫文儒雅好多<br />\n<br />\n仲有語尾又係屈機，XXはる=XXいる/する<br />\n<br />\n貓仔訓緊教：<br />\n猫が寝てはる<br />\n猫が寝ている<br />\n<br />\n前面京都腔淨係換咗一個字就比標準語優雅好多，感覺成件事輕鬆自在，冇標準語嘅束縛感<br />\n<br />\n正皮=京都弁<br />\n負皮=標準語"},{"pid":"e4ffcfdf1f1d420512d15bf4202e830a30b22ef8","tid":2131394,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/448QSu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F448QSu0.jpg&h=e6cb527c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20%動物成份"},{"pid":"658c57ed697f9bfccff147a78f983473ad7e6bf0","tid":2131394,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:02:32.000Z","msg":"21314"},{"pid":"747ae058c605d2712d3b05a367566382f5590aec","tid":2131394,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"噉京都腔點えぇぇぇ！？"},{"pid":"1024fb963cd403c466d0a4531af600422990f2ae","tid":2131394,"uid":69,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:04:52.000Z","msg":"其實姐係関西弁？"},{"pid":"ae23ed574ffcfe33b913e9fdf98c10f4920a559c","tid":2131394,"uid":55029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:04:55.000Z","ms